This product includes test fixtures and derived code from the following
projects:

1. Hasura GraphQL Engine V3 (https://github.com/hasura/graphql-engine)
   Copyright Hasura, Inc.
   Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
   - fixtures/lang-graphql/    (v3/crates/graphql/lang-graphql/tests)
   - fixtures/metadata-resolve/ (v3/crates/metadata-resolve/tests)
   - fixtures/execute/          (v3/crates/engine/tests/execute)
   - Portions of the source code in src/ are ported from the Rust
     implementation in v3/crates.

2. hasura/ndc-postgres (https://github.com/hasura/ndc-postgres)
   Copyright Hasura, Inc.
   Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
   - fixtures/ndc-postgres-translation/ (crates/query-engine/translation/tests)
